        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Distracted Driving Education Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Transportation (DOT) to establish a distracted driving education grant program under which DOT may make grants to nonprofit organizations to provide education to the public regarding the risks of distracted driving, including texting while driving. </p>]]>
        </text>
